{
  "name": "Panicked",
  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[starpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr/>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You drop everything you are holding and flee at top speed along a random path away from the source of your fear, as well as from any other dangers you encounter.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You can’t take any other actions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In addition, you take a –2 penalty to all ability checks, saving throws, and skill checks.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If cornered, you cower and don’t attack, typically using the total defense action in combat and nothing else.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You can use special abilities, including spells, to flee; indeed, you must use such means if they are the only way you have to escape.</p>",
